gomodel:SYNGO_2994  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.3: \"Dlg5 Is expressed in the postnatal brain and enriched in postsynaptic density fractions\"\n- \" DLG5 is highly enriched in PSD fractions in wild-type brains and the mutant DLG5LP protein, though present at lower levels than wild-type, retains its localization in the PSD fraction (Fig. 3G). These results show that DLG5 is a PSD component and that it is included in the PSD core protein-containing detergent-insoluble PSDIII fraction.\". Experimental description: - \"Freshly dissected mouse brains were homogenized in ice-cold 4 ....\"" ;
